# AutoMLOS Format String Database - 智能格式化版
# Format: message_id|format_string|description|message_type

# 传统系统消息 (0-9)
0|System started at timestamp %u|System startup message|0
1|System shutdown at timestamp %u|System shutdown message|0  
2|Service %u ready|Service initialization complete message|0
3|Service %u error: code %u|Service error message|0
4|Driver %u timeout after %u ms|Driver timeout message|0
5|Driver %u initialized successfully|Driver initialization message|0

# CAN总线消息 (6-9)
6|CAN frame received: ID 0x%X, DLC %u|CAN frame reception message|1
7|CAN frame transmitted: ID 0x%X, DLC %u|CAN frame transmission message|1
8|CAN bus error: code %u, severity %u|CAN bus error message|1
9|CAN configuration updated: baudrate %u, mode %u|CAN configuration change message|1

# UDS诊断消息 (10-19)
10|UDS request: SID 0x%X, DID 0x%X|UDS diagnostic request message|2
11|UDS response: SID 0x%X, result %u|UDS diagnostic response message|2
12|UDS session changed: from %u to %u|UDS session management message|2
13|UDS security access: level %u, status %u|UDS security access message|2
14|UDS routine control: routine %u, result %u|UDS routine control message|2

# AI推理消息 (20-29)
20|AI model switched: from %u to %u|AI model dynamic switching message|0
21|AI pipeline state changed: stage %u, status %u|AI pipeline state transition message|0
22|Multi-modal fusion completed: sources %u, confidence %u|Multi-sensor data fusion message|0
23|Model performance adapted: old_latency %u ms, new_latency %u ms|AI model performance adaptation message|0
24|Inference QoS adjusted: target %u%%, actual %u%%|AI service quality adjustment message|0

# 内核消息 (30-39)
30|Memory allocation: size %u, available %u|Memory management message|3
31|Scheduler context switch: from %u to %u|Process scheduling message|3
32|Interrupt handled: vector %u, latency %u|Interrupt processing message|3
33|System call: number %u, result %u|System call execution message|3
34|IPC message sent: type %u, size %u|Inter-process communication message|3

# 安全监控消息 (40-49)
40|Service graceful restart: pid %u, reason %u|Service controlled restart message|4
41|Fault recovery state: from %u to %u|Fault recovery state transition message|4  
42|System health assessment: score %u, trend %u|Dynamic health evaluation message|4
43|Resource isolation triggered: service %u, level %u|Service isolation for safety message|4
44|Safety monitor intervention: type %u, severity %u|Safety framework intervention message|4
45|Security violation: user %u, resource %u, action %u|Security access violation message|4
46|Permission check: user %u, operation %u, result %u|Permission verification message|4

# 动态资源管理消息 (50-59)
50|Service instance scaled: from %u to %u instances|Service dynamic scaling message|0
51|Compute resource allocated: service %u, cores %u|Dynamic resource allocation message|0
52|QoS policy updated: service %u, policy %u|Quality of service adjustment message|0
53|Load balancing triggered: source %u, target %u|Load distribution change message|0
54|Energy mode transition: from %u to %u|Power management state change message|0

# 跨域协同消息 (60-69)
60|Cross-service decision: services %u, consensus %u|Multi-service collaborative decision message|0
61|Distributed state sync: domain %u, version %u|Distributed state synchronization message|0
62|Fault tolerance activated: mechanism %u, level %u|Fault tolerance mechanism trigger message|0
63|Data consistency message: partition %u, status %u|Data consistency management message|0
64|Coordination protocol: phase %u, participants %u|Inter-service coordination message|0

# 诊断与调试消息 (70-79)
70|Diagnostic message: code %u, severity %u|Diagnostic message|0
71|Heartbeat from process %u|Heartbeat monitoring message|0
72|Performance profiling: service %u, metric %u|Performance measurement message|0
73|Debug trace: component %u, detail %u|Development debugging message|0
74|Configuration update: section %u, version %u|Runtime configuration change message|0